%% Data Flow Diagram: llama-stack-provider-trustyai-garak
%% Generated by: Claude Opus 4.6

sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as User/Client
    participant LLS as Llama Stack Server<br/>8321/TCP HTTP
    participant Provider as GarakRemoteEvalAdapter
    participant KFP as Kubeflow Pipelines API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant ValidatePod as KFP: validate_inputs Pod
    participant ScanPod as KFP: garak_scan Pod
    participant ParsePod as KFP: parse_results Pod
    participant vLLM as vLLM Inference<br/>OpenAI-Compatible API
    participant FilesAPI as Llama Stack Files API<br/>8321/TCP HTTP

    Note over Client,FilesAPI: Flow 1: Remote Scan Execution (Production)

    Client->>LLS: POST /v1/alpha/eval/run-eval<br/>Llama Stack auth
    LLS->>Provider: Delegate to Garak eval provider

    Provider->>KFP: Submit garak_scan_pipeline<br/>Bearer Token (OAuth/SA)
    KFP-->>Provider: Pipeline Run ID

    Provider-->>LLS: Job ID (async)
    LLS-->>Client: Job status: running

    KFP->>ValidatePod: Step 1: validate_inputs
    ValidatePod->>LLS: Check connectivity<br/>8321/TCP HTTP (cluster internal)
    LLS-->>ValidatePod: OK

    KFP->>ScanPod: Step 2: garak_scan
    ScanPod->>vLLM: Garak vulnerability probes<br/>HTTP/HTTPS, API Token
    vLLM-->>ScanPod: LLM responses
    ScanPod->>ScanPod: Convert results to AVID format
    ScanPod->>FilesAPI: Upload scan artifacts<br/>8321/TCP HTTP (cluster internal)
    FilesAPI-->>ScanPod: File IDs

    KFP->>ParsePod: Step 3: parse_results
    ParsePod->>ParsePod: Calculate TBSA metrics
    ParsePod->>ParsePod: Generate HTML report
    ParsePod->>FilesAPI: Upload parsed results<br/>8321/TCP HTTP (cluster internal)
    FilesAPI-->>ParsePod: File IDs

    Provider->>KFP: Poll run status<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+, Bearer Token
    KFP-->>Provider: Run complete

    Client->>LLS: GET /v1/alpha/eval/get-eval-job-result
    LLS->>Provider: Retrieve results
    Provider-->>LLS: Scan results + metrics
    LLS-->>Client: Vulnerability assessment report

    Note over Client,FilesAPI: Flow 2: Inline Scan Execution (Development)

    Client->>LLS: POST /v1/alpha/eval/run-eval
    LLS->>Provider: Delegate (inline mode)
    Provider->>Provider: Garak subprocess (local)
    Provider->>vLLM: Vulnerability probes<br/>HTTP/HTTPS, API Token
    vLLM-->>Provider: LLM responses
    Provider->>Provider: Parse results (in-process)
    Provider-->>LLS: Scan results
    LLS-->>Client: Vulnerability assessment report

    Note over Client,FilesAPI: Flow 3: Shield-Augmented Scan

    Client->>LLS: POST /v1/alpha/eval/run-eval<br/>(with shields configured)
    LLS->>Provider: Delegate with shield config
    Provider->>LLS: Safety API: run_shield (input)<br/>8321/TCP HTTP
    LLS-->>Provider: Shield verdict (input)
    Provider->>LLS: Inference API: chat.completions<br/>8321/TCP HTTP
    LLS-->>Provider: LLM response
    Provider->>LLS: Safety API: run_shield (output)<br/>8321/TCP HTTP
    LLS-->>Provider: Shield verdict (output)
